solver

Class SolverHeaders

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.SolverHeaders

  • public class SolverHeaders
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains declaration of all the headers used in the solver. For every SMT variable we append this header in order to generate name of the variable. For example, the variable name start time for task A0 will be "xA0" derived as (startTimeHeader + task name). It is convenient to modify headers only at one place
    Author:
    Pranav Tendulkar
